353
00:20:56,660 --> 00:20:58,299
Is Granny Caiyun all right?

354
00:20:58,300 --> 00:20:59,780
She's fine, just tired. Think about what happened.

355
00:20:59,780 --> 00:21:03,659
People have been taking photos with her all day long.

356
00:21:03,659 --> 00:21:05,440
She's old, so she's worn out.

357
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:09,260
It's the same with Uncle Xiangdong. He's having acupuncture in the hospital. For his arms.

358
00:21:15,180 --> 00:21:18,040
What's the matter with Na Na? She's asleep from exhaustion.

359
00:21:23,520 --> 00:21:26,480
I'm here to check in on you guys.

360
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:31,090
Based on the homestay reservations in town, this flood has passed.

361
00:21:31,090 --> 00:21:33,380
Even though there are many reservations next weekend,

362
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:36,010
tourists won't flood over like this.

363
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:40,940
If there's another wave, even I'll break down.

364
00:21:40,940 --> 00:21:42,780
It must've been hard on you guys.

365
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:48,540
Xiao Huang, you're here too!

366
00:21:48,540 --> 00:21:51,720
I'm here to thank you guys. What's wrong with your voice?

367
00:21:51,720 --> 00:21:55,080
I've been talking all day. So, my voice got hoarse.

368
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:58,819
No way. Why do you smell like that?

369
00:21:58,819 --> 00:22:00,580
Do I still smell like garbage?

370
00:22:00,580 --> 00:22:02,940
How much floral water did you spray on yourself?

371
00:22:02,940 --> 00:22:06,039
Not much. Just a little.

372
00:22:07,940 --> 00:22:09,880
Come here quickly.

373
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:12,240
Stop talking. Take a break.

374
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:13,800
I can help you clean up.

375
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:16,600
Don't do that. Your voice is already in this state.

376
00:22:16,600 --> 00:22:18,180
Drink some water.

377
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:20,880
You're in the line for the hospital.

378
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:22,720
Xiaochun, you should rest as well.

379
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:25,079
I'm fine. I'll tidy up.

380
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:32,500
Xiaochun, you don't seem very tired.

381
00:22:32,500 --> 00:22:35,600
Help Hongdou clean up.

382
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:39,000
I don't seem tired?

383
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:41,000
What made you think so?

384
00:22:41,000 --> 00:22:43,000
Go on.

385
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:44,700
Drink water.

386
00:22:45,700 --> 00:22:47,500
I'm not tired.

387
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:56,900
Old Xie, even you have someone who worries about you now.

388
00:22:59,400 --> 00:23:00,800
I'm going to use the megaphone

389
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,200
and make an announcement around the village.

390
00:23:02,200 --> 00:23:04,700
The village leaders will lead the whole village to pick up garbage and clean up.

391
00:23:04,700 --> 00:23:06,500
Are you coming?

392
00:23:06,500 --> 00:23:09,800
Tomorrow morning, I need to pay the temporary workers' wages.

393
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:11,600
I can't join you.

394
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:14,000
Okay, I won't bother you.

395
00:23:18,600 --> 00:23:21,600
What's the matter? Did you have a nightmare?

396
00:23:22,600 --> 00:23:24,600
You're drenched in sweat. Quick, drink some water.

397
00:23:24,600 --> 00:23:26,400
Have some water.

398
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,700
That's quite a thick stack.

399
00:24:29,700 --> 00:24:32,200
Uncle A'Yao, I'm here for my salary!

400
00:24:33,300 --> 00:24:34,800
Hongdou, you're also here.

401
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:37,200
- I came to hang out.
- Daxia.

402
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:39,300
I'm not done calculating Xiao Qin's wages. I'll calculate our dear Xiao Qin's one first.

403
00:24:39,300 --> 00:24:40,800
Dear Xiao Qin?

404
00:24:40,800 --> 00:24:43,400
If you want to woo me, get your number and line up.

405
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:46,100
Don't worry. I'll go when I'm done.

406
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:48,300
I'm not in a hurry. I'm free today.

407
00:24:48,300 --> 00:24:49,800
Is your shop closed today?

408
00:24:49,800 --> 00:24:51,900
Yeah. Even if I keep it open,

409
00:24:51,900 --> 00:24:54,200
my dad will say I'm wasting my time.

410
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:56,000
Xiao Qin's salary is ¥100 a day

411
00:24:56,000 --> 00:24:57,800
plus six hours of overtime pay.

412
00:24:57,800 --> 00:24:59,800
A total of ¥290.

413
00:24:59,800 --> 00:25:01,700
¥290.

414
00:25:01,700 --> 00:25:05,000
I'll round up the numbers for you. ¥300.

415
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:07,400
Uncle A'Yao, why have you become so generous?

416
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:10,200
You used to bargain with me just for light bulbs.

417
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:12,800
Being a consumer and a boss is different.

418
00:25:12,800 --> 00:25:14,500
That's a horse of another color.

419
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:19,400
I might as well work for you.

420
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:22,400
I didn't even earn ¥300 last week from selling goods.

421
00:25:23,600 --> 00:25:25,800
I want to buy a pair of shoes for Yang Zhinan.

422
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:29,000
Buy shoes for Yang Zhinan?

423
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:31,100
Have you ever bought shoes for your dad?

424
00:25:32,300 --> 00:25:35,200
I won't buy that for him. He scolds me all the time.

425
00:25:37,800 --> 00:25:40,200
Hongdou, when is your homestay recruiting staff?

426
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:42,200
Let me work as your service staff.

427
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,800
Don't be driven by impulse.

428
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:46,500
When your dad intended to close your sundry store,

429
00:25:46,500 --> 00:25:48,800
didn't you insist on keeping it open?

430
00:25:48,800 --> 00:25:50,500
I don't want to man a store.

431
00:25:50,500 --> 00:25:52,200
I just didn't want to learn embroidery.

432
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:54,500
I have nails under my butt, so I can't sit still.

433
00:25:54,500 --> 00:25:56,500
With your temper, you can't work as a service staff.

434
00:25:56,500 --> 00:25:58,700
What's wrong with my temper?

435
00:25:58,700 --> 00:26:00,200
If you meet impolite guests,

436
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:01,800
what should I do if you end up in a fight?

437
00:26:01,800 --> 00:26:03,500
I won't beat people up.

438
00:26:03,500 --> 00:26:05,300
At most, I'll quarrel with them.

439
00:26:05,300 --> 00:26:06,800
Besides, I'm very enthusiastic.

440
00:26:06,800 --> 00:26:09,400
I talk a lot. I can chat with anyone.

441
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:11,200
Even if foreigners come and there's a language barrier,

442
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:14,100
I can chat through gestures.

443
00:26:14,100 --> 00:26:15,900
Talkative. That's right.

444
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:17,300
You're talkative, too.

445
00:26:17,300 --> 00:26:18,800
I'm just a retailer of words, while you're a wholessaler.

446
00:26:18,800 --> 00:26:20,800
You blabber more than I do.

447
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:23,400
Be quiet. I'm calculating money.

448
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:24,700
He's calculating money.

449
00:26:24,700 --> 00:26:28,400
It's a plus if you're enthusiastic and chatty.

450
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:29,800
How about you think this through carefully?

451
00:26:29,800 --> 00:26:33,900
If you really wish to work at our homestay, let me know.

452
00:26:33,900 --> 00:26:36,000
We can discuss your salary.

453
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:38,000
You can join the staff training.

454
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:39,900
I've made my decision. I'll join you.

455
00:26:39,900 --> 00:26:41,200
Join what?

456
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:43,900
The renovation will take several months before the place will be open for business.

457
00:26:43,900 --> 00:26:46,200
During this period of time, think carefully.

458
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:48,960
If you really want to work there, discuss it with your parents. Sell the store.

459
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:52,400
I know! I'm not a three-year-old!

460
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:56,100
- By the way, can I bring Yang Zhinan over?
- Nope.

461
00:26:56,100 --> 00:26:57,700
He's very hardworking.

462
00:26:57,700 --> 00:27:00,300
- I only want you or Yang Zhinan. Just one.
- Why?

463
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:01,800
Well, you know why.

464
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:03,400
If you two are together, it'll be endless quarrels every day.

465
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:05,100
Will any work be done?

466
00:27:06,000 --> 00:27:07,300
That's true.

467
00:27:07,300 --> 00:27:11,100
Besides, I don't know if we'll still be a couple then.

468
00:27:11,100 --> 00:27:12,200
Let me tell you this.

469
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:14,300
He lied to me last time about heading home to sleep.

470
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:16,500
Turns out he went to an internet cafe and played games all night.

471
00:27:16,500 --> 00:27:19,000
That's preposterous! Break up right away!

472
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:20,600
Why are you like that?

473
00:27:20,600 --> 00:27:22,400
Why don't you break up with Sister Hongdou?

474
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:25,300
We don't quarrel. I don't lie to her.

475
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:28,499
Sister Hongdou, let me tell you this.

476
00:27:28,500 --> 00:27:32,000
When Uncle A'Yao was swimming in the reservoir as a kid, his clothes were stolen.

477
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:34,400
He went home naked.

478
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:38,000
That was Yang Guanjun.

479
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:40,000
Yang Guanjun?

480
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,400
Who's the one who enjoys drinking glycerine enema

481
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:46,000
and chewing table corners in class until a quarter of the table was gone?

482
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:47,200
Was that you?

483
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:49,500
That was Xie Qiang.

484
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:52,800
Xie Qiang?

485
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:54,700
Xiao Qin, don't fret. Take your time to consider.

486
00:27:54,700 --> 00:27:56,900
Think about all the embarrassing things Chairman Xie has done.

487
00:27:56,900 --> 00:27:58,800
I have plenty of time.

488
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:03,500
<i>Hu Youyu.</i>

489
00:29:10,600 --> 00:29:12,300
Come in.

490
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:18,600
Sister, why did you call me by my full name?

491
00:29:49,200 --> 00:29:51,000
What are you frying?

492
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:52,900
It smells good.

493
00:29:52,900 --> 00:29:55,600
Aunty A'Gui taught me this. Fried mushrooms.

494
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:58,600
I plan to make a few cans and send them to my daughter's school.

495
00:29:59,800 --> 00:30:01,800
For your daughter?

496
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:03,900
That's nice.

497
00:30:03,900 --> 00:30:06,300
You've been avoiding me for days.

